5 February 2010Media are invited to a cocktail function to be co-hosted by Government Communications (GCIS) and Primedia Broadcasting.This will provide media an opportunity to interact with government communicators ahead of the State of the Nation Address.The details of the cocktail function are as follows:Date: Wednesday, 10 February 2010Time: 18h30 for 19h00Venue: Primedia Broadcasting Studios Suite 7D, Somerset Square Highfield Road Green Point (Next door to Pigalle Restaurant)RSVP: Tuesday, 9 February 2010Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)